<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Image and Text Sections</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        .image {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .text {
            flex: 2;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="image1.jpg" alt="Image 1">
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            <h2>Section 1</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nullam ac urna vel dolor commodo sodales vel eu justo.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="image2.jpg" alt="Image 2">
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            <h2>Section 2</h2>
            <p>Integer cursus purus eget erat commodo, vel aliquam nisl fermentum. Duis in gravida elit, in commodo tortor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="image">
            <img src="image3.jpg" alt="Image 3">
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            <h2>Section 3</h2>
            <p>Aliquam nec ipsum non libero fermentum feugiat. In efficitur ultrices libero, eget varius felis eleifend eget.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
